OL,3,CMan appears in court after item
OL,4,Callegedly thrown at mosque window
OL,6,FA man has appeared in court charged
OL,7,Fwith racially aggravated criminal
OL,8,Fdamage after an item was allegedly
OL,9,Fthrown at a mosque window.
OL,11,FLuke Baulch, 43, appeared before
OL,12,FNewport Magistrates' Court and pleaded
OL,13,Fnot guilty to a charge of racially
OL,14,Faggravated criminal damage.
OL,16,FHe has been released on conditional
OL,17,Fbail ahead of a trial at Newport
OL,18,FMagistrates' Court on 22 November.
