OL,3,CMan appears in court after item
OL,4,Callegedly thrown at mosque window
OL,6,FGwent Police said the force received a
OL,7,Freport that "an item was thrown at a
OL,8,Fwindow of a mosque" in Shaftesbury
OL,9,FStreet, Newport, at around 7am on
OL,10,FThursday.
OL,12,FDeputy Chief Constable Mark Hobrough,
OL,13,Fof Gwent Police, said: "We will
OL,14,Fthoroughly investigate any alleged
OL,15,Foffence where racism or discrimination
OL,16,Fis an aggravating factor.
OL,18,F"Reports of this nature will be deeply
OL,19,Fconcerning for all our communities; my
OL,20,Fmessage to you is that we're here to
OL,21,Foffer support and keep you safe.
